text.tspan: Imports of goods and services, 1960 to 2022
Imports of goods and services represent the value of all goods and other market services received from the rest of
the world. Data are in constant U.S. dollars. This means values are corrected for inflation.
Data source: Multiple sources compiled by World Bank (2024)
